message: Rent life. Rent Your appartment, rent Your fridge, rent Your kitchen appliances, rent Your couch, rent Your computer, rent Your bed, rent Your toothbrush, return Your toothbrush, rent Your childrens schoolbooks, pay the lease on Your car, subscribe to a food delivery service. I want to create simple flash games for this website, i hope i will find the time for that.
